Group project 
CS547 Game design project 2
------------------------------

Team members:
Hua
Kuei-Ti 
Solongo

(1) Controls for the Game: 

Mouse left click on or dragging across standby tanks to select the tanks. 
Mouse left click on a non-occupied position to command selected tanks to move toward that position. 
Mouse left click on the opponent's entity to command selected tanks to move toward and attack that entity. 
Mouse left click on or dragging across non-standby tanks to command the tanks to stand by. 
Click a button on the panel to change the mode. 
In Repair Mode, click on an own entity to repair that entity. 
In Upgrade Mode, click on an own Level 1 tank factory or Level 1 defense wall to upgrade them to Level 2. 
In Wall Building Mode, click on an non-occupied position to build a Level 1 defense wall. 
In Factory Building Mode, click on an non-occupied position to build a Level 1 tank factory. 
In Tank Manufacture Mode, click on an own tank factory to manufacture a tank. 
	A Level 1 tank factory manufactures a Level 1 tank, and a Level 2 tank factory manufactures a Level 2 tank. 

(2) Cheat Codes: 

Mouse right click: Disable scrolling

